{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-introducing-yourself/grammar-highlights","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Potvrdi da sam pročitao/la važne gramatičke stvari.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-review-introducing-yourself","challengeType":31,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<h2>Konjugacija glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tener</span> u prezentu indikativu</h2>\n<p>Glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tener</span> (imati) se često koristi za razgovor o godinama na španskom.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Osoba</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Promene</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Značenje na engleskom</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Yo tengo</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">tengo</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Imam / Ja sam (po godinama)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tú tienes</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">tienes</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Ti imaš</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Standardna struktura za izgovaranje vašeg uzrasta je:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tengo</span> + broj + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">años</span>.</p>\n<p>Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tengo veintiocho años.</span> – Imam 28 godina.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Tengo treinta y seis años.</span> – Imam 36 godina.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h2>Nacija i rodni sporazumi</h2>\n<p>U Hispaniji, narodi moraju odgovarati spolu opisane osobe:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Muški rod imenice često završavaju sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-o</span> ili konsonantom.</li>\n<li>Ženski rod imenice često završavaju sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-a</span>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Primeri:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy chilena.</span> – Ja sam Mchile. (žensko)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy puertorriqueño.</span> – Ja sam Puerto Riko. (muški)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Soy uruguaya.</span> – Ja sam Muuruguayo. (žensko)</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h2>Pozdravi u zavisnosti od vremena dana</h2>\n<p>Španski pozdravi zavise od doba dana:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenos días.</span> – Dobro jutro.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas tardes.</span> – Dobar dan.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Buenas noches.</span> – Novosti za večer/noć.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ove su pristojne metode koje zavise od vremena kada započinjete razgovor.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Osnuti</h2>\n<p>Evo nekih uobičajenih načina za oproštaj na španskom:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Adiós</span> – Doviđenja.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hasta luego.</span> – Vidimo se kasnije.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hasta pronto.</span> – Vidimo se uskoro.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Hasta mañana.</span> – Vidimo sutra.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Chau</span> – Doviđenja (standardni swahili).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-introducing-yourself/grammar-highlights"},"questions":[],"scene":null,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","tests":[],"title":"Važne gramatičke stvari","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-review-introducing-yourself","dashedName":"grammar-highlights","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"es-a1-module-introducing-yourself","block":"es-a1-review-introducing-yourself","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-introducing-yourself/glossary","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-introducing-yourself/task-9","id":"68dc753010b6b271ac564e93","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":31,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-review-introducing-yourself/grammar-highlights"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}